{
  "page": "Feature quote/210",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Islander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Summer Islander\">My people</a> hold that there is no shame to be found in the <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">pillow house</a>. In the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>, those who are skilled at giving pleasure are greatly esteemed. Many highborn youths and <a href=\"/index.php/Virgin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Virgin\">maidens</a> serve for a few years after their <a href=\"/index.php/Flowering\" title=\"Flowering\">flowerings</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">honor the gods</a>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Chataya\" title=\"Chataya\">Chataya</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403185310\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 70/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 304/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--